{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_52_03",
  "title": "kana 3話 もしかして恋人？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、生き返る～。やっぱ冬に暖房ないとこ行くとか\nあり得ないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah~‚ I feel reborn~. Going somewhere without heating in winter\nis so stupid",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここ、バーですよね？　冷えた体を温めたいなら\n鍋とかを食べられるお店の方が良かったんじゃ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this a bar? You want to warm up your chilled body‚\nwouldn't a place with hot pot or something have been better?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな生温いもんじゃ、kanaの心は温まんないの\n高くて映えるカクテルじゃなきゃね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That kind of lukewarm thing‚ won't warm kana's heart\nOnly an expensive‚ photogenic cocktail is possible~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 26.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "……お、カクテルきた。へぇ、結構可愛いじゃん\nしかもちゃんと高そうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ the cocktail's here. Heh‚ it's pretty cute\nAnd it looks expensive too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 26.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-04.m4a",
          "delay": 2800.000000000001,
          "startTime": 29.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとテンション上がってきたかも～\n今日は沢山飲んじゃおっかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My tension might have risen a little~\nMaybe I'll drink a lot today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、それは良かったです……\nですがkanaさん……お酒はその、ほどほどにですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ that's good…\nBut kana-san… um please‚ drink in moderation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 50.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "あ？　何よ、そのバケモンを見るような顔\nあー、もしかしてmihoの酒癖のこと考えてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah? What's with that look on face‚ like seen a monster?\nAhー‚ are you thinking about miho's drinking habits?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 60.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あんな酒乱鬼軍曹と一緒にするなっての\nkanaはスマートに酒を嗜む、大人の女なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't compare that drunk monster?\nkana is a mature woman‚ who drinks smartly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "あとさぁ、せっかく綺麗なカクテルきたんだから\nkanaと一緒にさっさと撮れよ、使えねぇな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ there's a beautiful cocktail has arrived‚\nquickly take a picture with kana‚ you useless",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 76.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　……それにしても、kanaさんとお酒を\n飲むことって、あんまりないので嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes! …Anyway‚ I'm glad to see\nkana-san drinking‚ as I haven't really seen you do it often",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "こっちはあんたと酒飲んでも大して楽しくないんだから\n当たり前でしょ。ほら、早く何か面白い話しなさいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm don't really enjoy drinking with you‚\nit's only nature. Hey‚ tell me something interesting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 93.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "例えば～長瀬麻奈以外に気になる子の話とか？\nあ、遙子も昔から事務所にいたんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example~‚ how about someone you're interested in besides Mana Nagase?\nAh‚ Haruko has been with the office for a long time‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、アイドル相手にそんな感情を抱いたりしませんよ\n……あれ、さくらからメッセだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I don't have those kinds of feelings for idols\n…Huh‚ a message from Sakura",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.3333332999982,
          "startTime": 106
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（「ホテルの鍵が見当たらないんです」……！？）\n（俺も戻るか？　でも今はkanaさんと一緒だしなぁ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（「I can't find my hotel key」…!?）\n（Should I go back too? But‚ I'm with kana-san right now）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 118.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "誰からのメッセだよ？　何、もしかして恋人？\nちょっと見せて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who's message? Heh‚ is it your girlfriend?\nLet me see",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなんじゃありませんってば！　普通にさくらから\nですよ。ちょっとトラブルがあったみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not like that! It's just from Sakura.\nIt seems like there was a little trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2339130402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 130.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "なーんだ、つまんない。てか、さっきの話の続きだけど\nあんた浮いた話とかないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oohー‚ that's not funny. Anyway‚ continuing from earlier\nDon't you have any romantic stories?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、ありませんって！\nkanaさんの中で俺はどんなイメージなんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said‚ no!\nWhat kind of image do you have of me‚ kana-san!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 145.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
