      "text": "アイドル事務所のマネージャーの名刺で\n若い女の子に声かけまくる変態",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A pervert who approaches a young girl\nusing an idol agency manager's business card",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かに怜に声をかけたりしたこともありますが……\nですが、それは純粋な気持ちで……！　……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I definitely did speak to Rei once‚ though…\nBut‚ that was purely out of intention…! …Um?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6787280871,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
