      "text": "てか、さっきからめっちゃメッセきてんじゃん\nもしかして案外モテてたり？　ウケる～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ you've been getting so many messages for a while now\nMaybe you're popular than I thought? Cool~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.4093895912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、立て続けに連絡がきて……\nいったん通知オフにしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry‚ I've been getting messages one after another…\nI'll turn off notifications for now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
